{"tid":16377,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"怒插已婚男友7刀　女學護罪成判囚3年8個月　法官：愛情盲目但不","createTime":"2016-12-01T11:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T12:08:46.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f4f7d69a34db47f91fdab18b2e747e5bf67a772","tid":16377,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"已婚漢與女學護發展婚外情遭妻子揭發，二人分手後，女學護涉用8吋長餐刀怒插已婚漢背部和胸部共7刀。女學護早前被裁定4項有意圖而傷人及1項刑事恐嚇罪成，今在區域法院被判監3年8個月。<br />\n<br />\n辯方資深大律師駱應淦求情時引述被告簡媛茌（29歲）的心理和精神科醫生報告，指被告並沒有精神病和暴力傾向，又指被告遭遇坎坷，經歷遭前夫出賣、騙去父母金錢，又為了男事主鄭柏堯墮胎。辯方又指，相信被告在家人和朋友支持下，重犯機會不高。<br />\n暫委法官高偉雄判刑時指，無意對二人作道德和倫理的審判，惟被告在與事主交往前已知他已婚，雖然明白愛情可以很盲目，也知道被告憧憬與事主交往可彌補其感情缺失，卻事與願違，但法庭不能接受以暴力解決感情問題。法官認為被告並非在一時衝動下犯案，又指涉案的刀鋒銳利，未有對事主造成永久傷殘實屬幸運。<br />\n觀塘警區重案組第一隊督察許頌娸判刑後在庭外表示，案件源於感情糾紛，呼籲市民如有感情問題要盡快尋求協助，避免不愉快事情發生。<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161201/s00001/1480577002666SL4_86AC69884C173B88A854DFB7828DE559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161201%2Fs00001%2F1480577002666SL4_86AC69884C173B88A854DFB7828DE559.jpg&h=4b221ff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00001/1480564769390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00001%2F1480564769390&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=51a7ea63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00001%2F1480564769390&h=0f1057de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00001/1480564769390</a>"},{"pid":"d1ba4b4c489f2ef9f640e6c3447aa8cacb0eb3f2","tid":16377,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:01:33.000Z","msg":"29歲 (學護)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616d7834916ef994fb70054ffb9558bdc5e267f9","tid":16377,"uid":35034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"條女同條仔都幾似樣"},{"pid":"32ed18e46d84609c05c19d8bdad3cf3797c4466d","tid":16377,"uid":22680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條女同條仔都幾似樣</blockquote><br />\n其實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade7729c89fd2d438f23281daac9a92a0103d743","tid":16377,"uid":5716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咩 我睇落好似殺人犯個不老症"},{"pid":"a238c1bfb9338588aad6b0dd5b62dc7fc39f343e","tid":16377,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咩 我睇落好似殺人犯個不老症</blockquote><br />\n未審之前都有新聞有佢個樣啲巴絲話佢笑得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cab0de8c9cc53aa6bb0132d4cb4915041ea33b9","tid":16377,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:08:46.000Z","msg":"成件事最仆街係個男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  判個女朋友做乜"}]}